    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="论文"><a href="#论文" class="headerlink" title="论文"></a>论文</h2><h3 id="结构体"><a href="#结构体" class="headerlink" title="结构体"></a>结构体</h3><h4 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h4><p>500字左右。<br>内容包括：时间、作为项目经理参与了某某项目、项目投资额、工期、功能点、采用技术、项目型组织结构。</p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316213712.png"></p><h4 id="过渡"><a href="#过渡" class="headerlink" title="过渡"></a>过渡</h4><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316214335.png"></p><h4 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h4><h4 id="结尾"><a href="#结尾" class="headerlink" title="结尾"></a>结尾</h4><p>300字左右。<br>内容包括：项目已验收、不足之处（外部原因，可接受的不足）经过项目经理的纠偏未造成影响、表决心呼吁行动。</p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316214510.png"></p><h2 id="整合管理"><a href="#整合管理" class="headerlink" title="整合管理"></a>整合管理</h2><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314220646.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314220801.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314221013.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314221038.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314221208.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314221235.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314222742.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314223015.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314223113.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314223211.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240314223312.png"></p><h2 id="范围管理"><a href="#范围管理" class="headerlink" title="范围管理"></a>范围管理</h2><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317204324.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317204332.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317205208.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317205923.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317210230.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317210327.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317210405.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317211253.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317211346.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317211658.png"></p><p>投票：大多数、相对多数、一致同意、独裁。</p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317211940.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317212410.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317212607.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317212809.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317213701.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317213814.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317213931.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214100.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214111.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214352.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214454.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214624.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317214755.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317220422.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317220830.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317220853.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221127.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221549.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221725.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221734.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221924.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317221937.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240317222241.png"></p><h2 id="质量管理"><a href="#质量管理" class="headerlink" title="质量管理"></a>质量管理</h2><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316184948.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316185056.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316185527.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316185736.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316185918.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316190023.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316190313.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316190512.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316190722.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316190835.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316191000.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316191218.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316191619.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316192106.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316192347.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316192718.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316192934.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316193127.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316193218.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316193508.png"></p><blockquote><p>六西格玛（Six Sigma）是一种旨在通过消除缺陷、减少变异性和改善流程来提高业务和制造过程质量的管理策略。这个术语源于统计学中的西格玛等级，西格玛（σ）是衡量数据离散程度的一个标准差，而在六西格玛水平上，流程产出的缺陷率被控制在每百万机会中不超过3.4个。</p><p>六西格玛的核心理念是通过量化方法来驱动改进，它强调数据和统计分析在决策过程中的重要性。这种方法起源于20世纪80年代的摩托罗拉公司，并在随后的几十年中被其他许多组织采用，包括通用电气（GE）等知名公司。</p><p>六西格玛的实施通常涉及以下几个关键方面：</p><ol><li><p><strong>DMAIC</strong>：</p><ul><li>这是六西格玛最常用的流程改进方法，包括五个阶段：定义（Define）、测量（Measure）、分析（Analyze）、改进（Improve）和控制（Control）。这个过程旨在识别和消除流程中的问题，从而提高效率和质量。</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>DMADV</strong>：</p><ul><li>用于新产品或流程的设计和开发，包括五个阶段：定义（Define）、测量（Measure）、分析（Analyze）、设计（Design）和验证（Verify）。这个方法强调在设计阶段就考虑质量，以确保最终产品或流程满足质量要求。</li></ul></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote><p>1σ&#x3D;68%<br>2σ&#x3D;95%<br>3σ&#x3D;99%<br>6σ&#x3D; (100W-3.4)&#x2F;100W</p></blockquote><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316194226.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316194317.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316194418.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316194537.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316195059.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316195243.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316195623.png"></p><p><strong>可交付成果</strong>→质量控制→<strong>核实的可交付成果</strong>→范围确认→<strong>验收的可交付成果</strong>→移交</p><h2 id="沟通管理"><a href="#沟通管理" class="headerlink" title="沟通管理"></a>沟通管理</h2><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316200424.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316200710.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316201224.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316201350.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316201609.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316201806.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316201916.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316202013.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316202224.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316202753.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316202843.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316203024.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316203041.png"></p><blockquote><p>沟通渠道：n*(n-1)&#x2F;2</p></blockquote><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316203336.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316203411.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316211433.png"></p><p><img src="/../../images/Pasted%20image%2020240316211541.png"></p><p><img src="/.